S \subset\mathbb{R^2}, \;\;xSy \iff y=\left|\left(\frac13\right)^x-1\right|
(x, y) \in S \subset\mathbb{R^2}, \;\;xSy \iff y=\left|\left(\frac13\right)^x-1\right|,\quad x, y \in \mathbb{R}
y = \left|\left(\frac13\right)^x-1\right|
x = \left|\left(\frac13\right)^y-1\right|
x = y
y = \left|\left(\frac13\right)^x-1\right|
\left|\left(\frac13\right)^y-1\right|
z = \left|\left(\frac13\right)^x-1\right|
